Angel Prime 




He started flying after Aerotaur. then he heard Magnus com and he 
respond. "Hey magnus I am no longer with the maximals. just talked to 
Prowl or Ironraptor." He activated his heat sensor and spotted 
Aerotaur. He flew above Aerotaur. "your Guardian Angel his here." He 
smiled and waited for Recon to arrive.
